reviewText: I just love this DVD. I am so thankful that I was able to source this at the steal of a deal It is more than earning its keep. I have fun while keeping fit
my cd player is not reading it. All cds a bought from walmart and other store are perfectly working but thiis one is not.
Received this DVD just as described and in excellent condition.  I have been looking for this for months without having to buy the entire set as this is a replacement.

This is a fun workout with easy to follow instructions and even a cooldown.  I worked up a nice sweat and the time flew by.  I use it to rotate with my other workouts and I look forward to doing this one.  I only needed the dvd set because I had the weights from another Zumba workout set.
It works fine and I have no complaints.
Received the dvd set on time and in good condition. this replaced the set I used to have and was exactly what I was looking for.  Thanks!
